item.title: [HIVE-22537] getAcidState() not saving directory snapshot causes multiple calls to S3 api
item.description: Fix for HIVE-21225 is not enabled in query coordinator codepath. The last argument (generateDirSnapshots) for getAcidState() is set to false when invoked by callInternal(). Also, snapshot is not used for file exists calls.
item.summary: getAcidState() not saving directory snapshot causes multiple calls to S3 api

status.description: The issue is considered finished, the resolution is correct. Issues which are not closed can be reopened.
